00:30:28.271 --> 00:30:39.479
It was so beautiful and so detailed. It changed me. But as it kept going, I heard, 'Woe, woe, woe, America.

00:30:39.480 --> 00:30:53.936
Woe, woe, woe, Miami. Woe, woe, woe, Los Angeles.'I saw a tsunami wave coming. I saw great destruction coming.

00:30:53.937 --> 00:31:01.708
