00:31:01.709 --> 00:31:10.159
As I was looking into this vision that the Lord was allowing me to see, I saw dead fish everywhere.

00:31:10.160 --> 00:31:22.519
I have never seen anything like this before. The very waters were all polluted with a red sludge.

00:31:22.520 --> 00:31:32.559
There were so many dead fish, whales, octopus—all of it. Everything was floating on the top.

00:31:32.560 --> 00:31:43.678
Disgusting. All dead. It was as far as the eye could see. It wasn't just on the shoreline, but they were dead all throughout the water.

00:31:43.679 --> 00:31:51.393
The water was littered with dead fish. I don't think any of them were alive.

00:31:51.394 --> 00:32:07.017
In the vision, I saw islands: Haiti, Jamaica, Grand Cayman, all of them. I was looking toward the south-southeast.

00:32:07.018 --> 00:32:17.893
As I was looking down, I could see the people, and there was so much stench and a raw flesh smell.

00:32:17.894 --> 00:32:24.232
People were so sick on those islands because of all the dead fish.

00:32:24.233 --> 00:32:36.860
It was causing disease and the smell. You could smell it in the vision. That's how tangible this vision was.

00:32:36.861 --> 00:32:44.359
I could see the dead fish washing on the shore, and the government didn't know what to do with them.

00:32:44.360 --> 00:32:47.544
People didn't know what to do because they were all washing in and you couldn't control it.

00:32:47.545 --> 00:33:03.134
There were literally hundreds of millions, if not billions, of dead fish everywhere—even Hawaii, Honolulu.

00:33:03.135 --> 00:33:10.398
I saw it all over. Then I saw Mark Zuckerberg, but his hair was a lot puffier.

00:33:10.399 --> 00:33:19.529
He was down in a bunker in the middle of the island. He was down in a fraidy hole, like a silo.

00:33:19.530 --> 00:33:30.042
I could see lights on around him. But as I panned across, the Lord allowed me to see people hiding in caves.

00:33:30.043 --> 00:33:49.658
I heard, 'The great and terrible day of the Lord.'Suddenly, I saw farmers, and they had their overalls, but all the land was not producing. There was great drought and famine.

00:33:49.659 --> 00:34:10.435
I could see them looking toward the south and the east, but they had a discouragement upon their faces like, 'What are we going to do?'As I looked to the sky, I saw the sky all around us was on fire.

00:34:10.436 --> 00:34:23.398
There was smoke and ash and flame in the air from volcanoes that were going off everywhere.

00:34:23.399 --> 00:34:35.999
