00:35:58.693 --> 00:36:17.804
The entire being of the angel was rain, a storm, and there was a major waterfall coming out of them, pouring into the ocean.

00:36:17.805 --> 00:36:26.474
I knew they were angels. Their faces had no features—it was just black around their eyes.

00:36:26.475 --> 00:36:33.290
You could get lost in that darkness. I've never seen anything like it.

00:36:33.291 --> 00:36:43.768
I saw one angel take a long pipe from his hand and put it to his lips.

00:36:43.769 --> 00:37:02.447
As he blew into this horn-looking thing, I said, 'It doesn't look like a ram's horn, like a shofar.'It was a long piece of golden pipe.

00:37:02.448 --> 00:37:19.540
As he blew into it, the whole earth shook. Not just one place had an earthquake, but as he blew into this horn, all of the earth shook at once.

00:37:19.541 --> 00:37:28.639
I heard the scripture: 'The earth will rock and reel like a drunkard.'The whole earth was trembling.

00:37:28.640 --> 00:37:36.399
He said, 'There will be no place to hide to escape the wrath to come, son.

00:37:36.400 --> 00:37:46.599
For they will hide in the caves and in their ditches, and they will not get away from the wrath which is to come.

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:59.479
For this is the great and terrible day of the Lord.'As I looked across, I could see all of New York burning with fire.

00:37:59.480 --> 00:38:06.576
