00:39:04.417 --> 00:39:21.695
I told Diana, 'I'm going to meditate on this more and pray. Don't be so quick to make videos.'I had to process what I'd seen. I saw those angels and they really tripped me out.

00:39:21.696 --> 00:39:46.599
Diana said, 'I want to read Revelation to you, chapter 8.'She said there were four angels, and seven altogether, but four first and then three for a later time.

00:39:46.600 --> 00:39:52.751
