00:39:52.752 --> 00:40:04.519
All I know is I saw these angels blowing these horns and all this stuff going on."She goes, "Do you think it was the four coming out of the Euphrates River because they were water?"So, I don't know.

00:40:04.520 --> 00:40:20.319
