00:40:54.120 --> 00:41:09.199
It was something upon the water. It sounded like you hear a tornado or a freight train.

00:41:09.200 --> 00:41:18.311
You can hear a train coming in the distance—that loud train coming, not the horn.

00:41:18.312 --> 00:41:30.106
It sounded like a loud noise, but it was deafening. It was so loud, and it was on the face of the water of the world.

00:41:30.108 --> 00:41:53.399
The seas and the waves were roaring. It was loud; it was a noise. All I know to tell you is that we're running out of time.

00:41:53.400 --> 00:42:04.399
