Thank you, Lord, that you've given me a fresh, clean start in Jesus'mighty name.

00:48:09.282 --> 00:48:16.319
Amen."I believe if you just said that prayer, you just got born again.

00:48:16.320 --> 00:48:21.420
Now, what do you do? You find a Bible-believing church. My wife and I go to a non-denominational church.

