They go and they disappear like that. Every single time. And I think that's pretty cool.

00:53:23.803 --> 00:53:32.356
I always look at it and go, 'Man, when I'm looking at that vision, I'm like, what are those doves doing?'But they all are spinning and they're circling and they like this thing.

